{"tid":2443116,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大陸年底債務頻爆雷 Q4信用債評等下調比例近8成","createTime":"2021-03-12T00:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T05:47:49.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7b232682c30ec229d8ef85a90193b2c59e542a","tid":2443116,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T00:33:00.000Z","msg":"大陸年底債務頻爆雷 Q4信用債評等下調比例近8成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210311001991-260410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20210311001991-260410&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw063eTsi4ka8iUmrXsVTuNg%3D&h=7f00eaf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20210311001991-260410</a><br />\n<br />\n大陸2020年底頻傳企業債務違約危機，最新數據顯示，光是2020年第四季，存續的公司信用類債券公開發行主體評等級別共下調35次，占比接近全年8成。<br />\n<br />\n中國銀行間市場交易商協會和中國證券業協會11日公布的第四季債市信用評級機構業務通報顯示，2020年第四季，評等級別下調35次，涉及發行人21家。整個2020年，評等級別下調次數共有127次，涉及發行人80家。<br />\n<br />\n而截至2020年底，存續的公司信用類債券公開發行主體共計3,894家，較2019年同期增加215家。<br />\n<br />\n2020年第四季有包括華晨、永煤等不少知名國企違約，引爆信用債風險，也影響至今公司債發行狀況。"},{"pid":"d9950bf84cdcb308a9396dd6a5ff0f45e1eaf4b0","tid":2443116,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:03:31.000Z","msg":"熱身前既熱身運動姐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />年中之後好睇"},{"pid":"a0e0d0b0da0667ea57f8aae35fac20ee57935c11","tid":2443116,"uid":40267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:04:45.000Z","msg":"內債定外債先<br />\n前者wfc"},{"pid":"92ff960fe27de1126bae8626d626b00cd76aeccf","tid":2443116,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"有香港外匯同MPF未驚過啦"},{"pid":"22d69495169e2fbb7c1198c2d1453889a0583c87","tid":2443116,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqzXWtS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?